title: Night of the Hunted (1980)...........FFF
description: Cult French sex-horror director Jean Rollin created this oddity in 1980. This one is a strange departure from his usual vampire-themed fare: In a strange future society, the residents of an apartment building suffer from collective amnesia and insanity, resulting in extreme sex and violence (a la David Cronenberg&#039;s SHIVERS and J.G. Ballard&#039;s novel HIGH RISE). A strange and interesting curiosity for those with a tolerance for gore.
